reviewText: This DVD WOULDN'T PAY AT ALL ON ANY DVD PLAYER WE TRIED JUST TO BE SURE. NOT HAPPY AT ALL HOPING THAT THE REST OF THE OTHERS I ORDERED ARE NOT LIKE THIS ONE. SO DISAPPOINTED.
Funny!  Arrived ahead of time, live this DVD.

Mrs. Brown's Boys is the best comedy in years!  Be prepared for the language content to be a little raw at times, but it doesn't take away from the comedy, it actually makes it funnier most of the time.  I love this series!

For those who have never watched Mrs Brown's Boys all I can say is that I truly feel sorry for you.  She is a foul mouth mother with the best of intentions.  I can see why this is one the most popular shows in Ireland and England.  I just don't understand why they don't show the series in the US.
